posts.post_title: FS T210 Series 5 & 7 Lots on Ebay
posts.post_content: Been away for awhile, but maybe there are some niche collectors out there that are into the T210's.  Over 50% of both series sets ( 5 & 7) up for auction on Ebay.  Just look under mintbid in community to see lots.  Thanks.
